<sect>Introduction
<p>

KMines is the classical Minesweeper game. 

You must discover all the cases without a mine to win: 

<itemize>
<item>Left-button will uncover a case. 
<item>Right-button will mark a case as containing a mine or as being uncertain. 
<item>Middle-button will try to clear the eigth surrounding cases if there are the right number of cases already marked as containing a mine. 
<item>Pressing the smiley will start a new game.
</itemize>


